{"tid":2088330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（海外戰綫）一齊做紅色愛國好青年- 中華人民共和國公職人員政務處分法（自2020年7月1日起施行）","createTime":"2020-07-01T05:38:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T05:38:03.000Z","uid":131888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"578f0ccc365f207485aa201fd0bc8ba50c308cd0","tid":2088330,"uid":131888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T05:38:03.000Z","msg":"中華人民共和國公職人員政務處分法<br />\n（本法自2020年7月1日起施行）<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.moj.gov.cn/Department/content/2020-06/22/592_3251129.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.moj.gov.cn%2FDepartment%2Fcontent%2F2020-06%2F22%2F592_3251129.html&d=oa%2BbSijZO%2BDWYSsAyiffbskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=def6fc27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.moj.gov.cn/Department/content/2020-06/22/592_3251129.html</a><br />\n<br />\n第三十一條 違反規定出境或者辦理因私出境證件的，予以記過或者記大過；情節嚴重的，予以降級或者撤職。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">違反規定取得外國國籍或者獲取境外永久居留資格、長期居留許可的，予以撤職或者開除。</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}